@sbodenstein MKL with v0.11 is quite buggy. I often got `inf` values during training for no obvious reason (i.e. training is stable without mkl / on GPU).
I'm not sure about v0.12 due to https://github.com/apache/incubator-mxnet/issues/8280 .

(i.e. even without MKL-DNN MKL is buggy)

I would like this to be included in 1.0.
Please review for accuracy and completeness.
@mli @piiswrong @nswamy
